<p>####</p>
<ol>
  <li>A CMake-based buildsystem is organized as a set of high-level logical
targets.</li>
  <li>Each target corresponds to an executable or library.</li>
  <li>Dependencies between the targets are expressed in the buildsystem to
determine the build order and the rules for regeneraton to change</li>
</ol>

